com.acsredux.adapter.mailgun
The MailGun adapter sends member email notifications using https://www.mailgun.com.
com.acsredux.adapter.stub
The Stub adapter provides an in-memory implementation of persistance and notification ports.
com.acsredux.adapter.web
The Web adapter renders an HTML interface to the core business objects.
com.acsredux.core.admin
The Admin core defines the services, data types, and ports for site administrators.
com.acsredux.core.base
The Base core contains code that is shared across all core modules.
com.acsredux.core.members
The Member core defines the services, data types, and ports for site members.
com.acsredux.lib.env
The Env library helps other modules load their configuration from environmental variables.
